snippet.title: Visual Pinball X VR - (Oculus Rift/Oculus Link Quest) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
We try some tables on this pinball emulator/simulator:

WWF Royal Rumble
The Simpsons 
Simpsons Pinball Party
Super Mario Brothers 
Super Mario Bros. Mushroom World
Bugs Bunny Birthday Ball
Independance Day ID4
Back To The Future
